1. *Poslom* je stekao nova znanja. (He acquired new knowledge through the job.) 
2. On je bio veoma uspešan u *poslu*. (He was very successful in the job.)
3. Ona se nada da će dobiti dobar *posao*. (She hopes to get a good job.)
4. On je završio *posao*. (He finished the job.)
5. Oni su bili veoma zadovoljni njegovim *poslom*. (They were very pleased with his job.)
6. Ona se bavi *poslom* od svoje dvadesete godine. (She has been working since her twenties.)